{"tid":379723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★飛磚殺人：新移民：呻地盤工作辛苦 地盤無升降機搭","createTime":"2017-08-29T14:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T04:30:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a335be87d06534d31c0bb83422ccef0e28077465","tid":379723,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:38:14.000Z","msg":"慘死的「輝哥」<span style=\"color: red;\">5年前與妻子來港定居，雖然年過60，但無其他技能，只能做體力勞動搵食</span>。輝哥曾向妻子訴說工作辛勞，曾透露在大廈地盤工作，因無升降機搭，試過徒步走上28層樓前往樓上工地，儘管如此，輝哥一直頂硬上。其妻今日由警方通知丈夫死訊後，由數名友人陪同趕到醫院，離開時低頭啜泣。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，輝哥一家5口原居內地，2012年夫婦成功申請來港，獲派慈雲山慈民邨公屋，3名年約30歲的兒子則留在內地。輝哥在玻璃幕牆公司做雜工，穿梭於各個地盤工作，負責「搬搬抬抬」及雜務工作，日薪約700港元。他約一個月前被調派至大嶼山人工島工作，今日調回到長沙灣地盤上班，詎料送命。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170829/bkn-20170829142545435-0829_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170829%2Fbkn-20170829142545435-0829_00822_001.html&d=YOVUTJKCNKRQH9lb%2FzAM%2F6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=8eecbd93\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170829/bkn-20170829142545435-0829_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fd5cd75513a57158fb2e4d596d993a5fe7deabb6","tid":379723,"uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:38:41.000Z","msg":"一家5口原居內地，2012年夫婦成功申請來港，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">獲派慈雲山慈民邨公屋</span>"},{"pid":"7c3e7e8717be0bc273d1b22604beed9bbb1687c9","tid":379723,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4438f84d5d8ab1891723e8be116ee23cde5aa6d","tid":379723,"uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T14:41:18.000Z","msg":"same<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.es